Steve Harvey once again commands the stage in his 90 minute stand-up
comedy concert Im Still Trippin. Harvey kept it clean and
family friendly in his last comedy special Dont TripHe Aint
Through With Me Yet. Not easy for one of the Original Kings of
Comedy, but then Harveys versatility is precisely why hes in a
class of his own. In Im Still Trippin Harvey never misses a
beat and no topic is off limits. Harvey takes you on a ride through
his personal experiences as it pertains to his family, work and
traveling. Filmed in New Jersey to a full house, his energy and
comedic timing are second to none. This comedic performance is sure
to become an instant classic.
